text: Winnie Harlow has modeled for Marc Jacobs, Coach, Elie Saab, and tons of other big - name designers and fashion houses. But little do fans know, the 23 - year - old ’ s introduction to the modeling industry was actually on Tyra Banks ‘ s reality TV competition, “ America ’ s Next Top Model. ” On a recent episode of Andy Cohen ‘ s “ Watch What Happens Live, ” Harlow opened up about her time on reality TV, and let ’ s just say, she isn ’ t exactly pleased with people who credit “ ANTM ” as her big break.
